name: GOTM
description: GOTM Labz provides a range of tools to help web3 project founders deliver innovative solutions, including NFT Staking, Trait Management, Reward Systems. GOTM is the token that powers the tools. GOTM Labz is focused on the Solana eco-system, due to the scalability, cheap tx costs, high security. GOTM Labz makes it easy for anyone to deploy robust, powerful and scalable solutions with ease to the solana blockchain to build communities with rewards and incentives.
